snippet.title: Sad News, Shannen Doherty Reveals She Has Only Few Days To Live After His Battle With Stage 4 Cancer
snippet.description:
Shannen Maria Doherty is an American actress. She is known for her roles as Jenny Wilder in Little House on the Prairie, Maggie Malene in Girls Just Want to Have Fun, Kris Witherspoon in Our House, Heather Duke in Heathers, Brenda Walsh in Beverly Hills, and again in and Prue Halliwell in Charmed.
